  "texts": [
    "Token sequences for free-text were generated using our domain-specific tokenizer.",
    "We named the model trained under this task only as PCa-LLM.",
    "In phase II of training, we aimed for the model to learn clinical language specific to prostate cancer.",
    "As described earlier, we marked clinical terms in free-text data of prostate cancer patients using UMLS parser.",
    "In this phase of training, we used masked clinical token prediction as a self-supervised training task."
